Ok, that makes sense. How about simply returning `int` instead of `bool` from `AppInit*`?
And then

```
        int ret = AppInitRPC(argc, argv);
        if (ret != -1)
            return ret;
```

This option seems a bit cleaner to me and should do the trick, see 0f9d7b6.

